Somizi and Mohale are making a difference in people's lives. The couple announced this morning on Twitter that hey would give R500 to ten people, who commented with their numbers on Twitter. This Somizi said was to make the world a better place through their foundation Somhale Foundation. The couple's kind gesture comes at a time when South Africans are hard hit by the coronavirus, which has wreaked havoc in people's lives. @SomhaleF making the world a better place one person at a time....good luck," tweeted the media personality. Good morning.....myself amd my husband @mohale_motaung wud like put a smile on the faces of the first ten ppl to inbox their numbers so we cud ewallet R500 each through our foundation @SomhaleF making the world a better place one person at a time....good luck  